tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  36,57,"Theirs the fruit) different kinds of fruit (and theirs (all) that they ask) and desire;"
  36,58,"(The word from a Merciful Lord (for them) is: Peace) they are greeted with the greeting of peace!"
  36,63,"(This is hell which you were promised) in the life of the world."
  36,64,"(Burn therein this day for that you disbelieved) in it and also because of your denial of the Scriptures and the messengers."